    "name": "Infect Cam",
    "steam_appid": 3168930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/2ba4d33e13407bd6cdc8feafbc41c923.avif?t=1768248559\" width=780 height=80 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在疫情后的十年里，人类人口锐减至数百万。数十亿人死亡，但只有极少数真正长眠不醒……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这个黑暗的世界里，我们的营救小队执行人质营救任务，只为救出哪怕一个人。在偶然发现一条线索后，他们将被卷入黑暗深处，寻求一丝光明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/fda28fc33fadb8f1df90dc47acd0e356.poster.avif?t=1768248559\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/fda28fc33fadb8f1df90dc47acd0e356.webm?t=1768248559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Infect Cam</strong>：一场高风险、充满肾上腺素的生存体验。你和四人小队将面对数量远超的敌人，管理有限的资源，追寻可能改变人类命运的希望……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/b6cc86498623cc9ec3c31ab84f2f2f83.poster.avif?t=1768248559\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/b6cc86498623cc9ec3c31ab84f2f2f83.webm?t=1768248559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/2c3f5221851ec3b5b9590061a1f85257.avif?t=1768248559\" width=780 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每支救援小队由四人组成。没有人能独自生还，但合作就有希望。沟通、协作、分享资源，相互信任，提高生存几率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/67f7b7e6468fc405a22d737e0678c403.poster.avif?t=1768248559\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/67f7b7e6468fc405a22d737e0678c403.webm?t=1768248559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/a403e01aa4ed85d632984a54770dc83b.avif?t=1768248559\" width=780 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一刻都至关重要。每颗子弹、每个医疗包、每位队友都可能决定成败。从第一人称视角体验生存挣扎，视野受限，快速决策，搜集补给，你的选择决定队伍的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/544661340ce941b6a2be29bf27dbc53b.poster.avif?t=1768248559\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/544661340ce941b6a2be29bf27dbc53b.webm?t=1768248559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3168930/extras/ee05e9a2a1f6b4a25dbf8b1c28d611c5.avif?t=1768248559\" width=780 height=80 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每座城市都有不同的挑战。务必保持队形。走散就等于死亡。深入未知后，那些隐藏真相的人将追踪你。做好准备，因为末日伊始，没人欢迎你的到来。</p>",
